Take the knife from the table.

Take the piece of lettuce from the table.

Put the lettuce into the sink and washed it.

high_descs: Turn left and head towards the wall, then turn right and go ahead to the next wall, turning left again and going down the hall, entering the last door on the left and approaching the desk.
Pick up the knife from the desk.
Exit the room the way you came in, then turn right and go back down the hall until reaching the kitchen on the left, approaching the lettuce.
Slice the head of lettuce that is on the corner of the counters next to a clock.
Look to the microwave on the left.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Look back towards the cut up lettuce on the countertop.
Take one piece of lettuce from the bowl.
Return to the sink you came from and go straight ahead to the door on the end.
Wash the lettuce inside the sink with water and pick the lettuce back up.
Return to the microwave in the kitchen.
Put the lettuce in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cut and washed lettuce into the microwave.
